---
title: Slow-Cooker Chipotle Pork Sloppy Joes on Brioche Buns with Carrot Raisin Slaw
description: Don’t you wish you could just press play on a recipe and let dinner assemble itself? Guess what: it’s possible with a slow cooker. Break out the machine for these family-friendly sloppy joes, which feature a chipotle pork filling on a brioche bun and are accompanied by a crisp carrot raisin slaw. They’re so simple, all you have to do is put your ingredients inside the cooker base and let the magic happen. Just make sure to plan ahead—the cooking takes 6-8 hours depending on the heat setting.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/slow-cooker-chipotle-pork-sloppy-joes-8a73ecc7.jpg
